Hypothesis testing is about claim verification in the business. 

 

Z test  

T test  

Anova 

ChisQ 

1. Z test: 

Sigma is give  

Cv=stats.norm.isf(alpha) 

One sample Z test  

Test stat= xbar- mew/sigma/sqrt(n) 

 

T Test 

Sigma is unknown 

Cv= stats.t.isf(Alpa) 

Test stat = xbar-mew/s/sqrt(n) 

ONE SAMPE Z TEST  

Here pop mean and pop sd is given 

Test stat=xbar-mew /sigma/sqrt(n) 

 

ONE SAMPLE T TEST 

Here Pop mean and sample sd is given 

Test stats= stats.test_1smp(data, df) 

Formula = xbar-mew/s/sqrt(N) 

 
